world.story

Class QuestTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • world.story.QuestTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatabaseManager.DatabaseTable

    public class QuestTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements DatabaseManager.DatabaseTable
    Contains the SQL schema for creating a table for storing quest information. Quests are instanced, so this does not have any way to link a quest to a player, only to get general info on the quest.
